WEBVTT

00:05.773 --> 00:08.540
 They say every cop has two...

00:08.576 --> 00:10.843
<i>The case that makes you... </i>

00:11.607 --> 00:15.547
<i>... pushes you to your limits,
earns you that badge.</i>

00:17.384 --> 00:20.686
<i>And the one that breaks you.</i>

00:21.610 --> 00:23.409
<i>Rips it all apart.</i>

00:25.413 --> 00:27.446
<i>Tears you to shreds.</i>

00:30.385 --> 00:32.418
<i>Sometimes... </i>

00:34.054 --> 00:36.289
<i>... they're the same case.</i>

