thought about your boy...

20:26.212 --> 20:27.578
Your beautiful little boy.

20:29.548 --> 20:30.914
I wished I did it.

20:30.949 --> 20:33.283
I wished I took him
from you and hurt him,

20:33.319 --> 20:35.152
wrapped my fingers around his throat

20:35.188 --> 20:37.021
and watch the life drip
from his little body,

20:37.056 --> 20:38.022
bit by bit.

20:38.996 --> 20:42.191
So don't feel sorry
about what happened to me.

20:42.226 --> 20:45.094
I didn't spend a minute feeling sorry

20:45.130 --> 20:46.997
for what happened to you.

20:51.236 --> 20:53.436
Price of coffee's not
what it used to be.

21:07.251 --> 21:08.750
 Why didn't you run?

21:11.055 --> 21:13.787
I mean, for 10 years,

21:13.823 --> 21:16.157
some crazy dude had you
locked up in a basement.

21:16.192 --> 21:19.041
He had to bring you
food every day, right?

21:19.077 --> 21:20.061
I mean, he must have messed up

21:20.096 --> 21:22.196
and forgot to lock
the door once or twice.

21:22.232 --> 21:24.165
Why... Why didn't you just...

21:25.123 --> 21:27.135
