21:35.746 --> 21:37.044
Yesterday.

21:40.749 --> 21:42.382
I'm... I'm...

21:42.418 --> 21:44.851
I'm sorry, dude.

21:44.886 --> 21:46.153
I was...

21:46.188 --> 21:47.553
Hey, Danny.

21:47.588 --> 21:49.121
How does it get in there?

21:50.850 --> 21:51.984
What?

21:53.213 --> 21:54.549
The ship.

21:57.265 --> 21:58.997
