22:02.370 --> 22:03.830
What if it's not him?

22:04.176 --> 22:06.504
I know. I know that sounds
crazy, and maybe it is.

22:06.540 --> 22:08.906
But he is... different, okay?

22:08.942 --> 22:10.675
From the moment I saw
him at the hospital,

22:10.710 --> 22:12.975
there's just been
something off about him.

22:13.713 --> 22:15.046
H-he's different.

22:15.082 --> 22:17.449
