- No, no.

22:17.484 --> 22:18.616
Just listen to me, because...

22:18.651 --> 22:22.252
Adam's different because
he's not 9 years old anymore,

22:22.288 --> 22:23.853
because he eats eggs.

22:23.889 --> 22:25.255
Uh, the... the ships!

22:25.291 --> 22:26.423
In the bottles?

22:26.459 --> 22:28.959
