How could he forget that?

22:32.264 --> 22:34.198
Maybe it was the decade
of rape and torture.

22:34.233 --> 22:35.199
Willa...

22:35.234 --> 22:37.234
They did a DNA test,
you worthless piece of...

22:37.269 --> 22:38.601
That's enough!

22:49.347 --> 22:51.280
You are my son...

22:51.316 --> 22:53.876
And I will always love you.

22:54.519 --> 22:58.086
But you... are a drunk, honey.

22:58.122 --> 23:01.658
And it's my fault for
cleaning up after you.

23:01.693 --> 23:04.759
But... you are just a drunk.

23:05.404 --> 23:06.393
Mom...

23:06.430 --> 23:09.895
Yeah, you're a drunk,
and you are confused.

23:11.301 --> 23:18.894
