23:34.822 --> 23:36.289
<i>It was up on the ceiling.</i>

23:36.324 --> 23:38.124
<i> His skin looks like gravel.</i>

23:38.160 --> 23:39.626
<i>He has holes in his face.</i>

23:39.661 --> 23:41.494
