27:58.907 --> 28:00.361
Oh, god.

28:01.209 --> 28:02.645
I am so sorry.

28:04.445 --> 28:06.909
Are you?

28:07.447 --> 28:09.248
Well, come on, I didn't
know he was there.

28:10.284 --> 28:11.216
Oh, please. Come on.

28:11.252 --> 28:12.851
You... you got a sixth sense.

28:12.887 --> 28:13.925
Don't... That's not fair!

28:13.950 --> 28:17.355
Hey, I-I get it.
Adam won you City Council.

28:17.391 --> 28:19.224
Why not governor this time
around? Even president.

28:19.260 --> 28:21.593
"Mayor puts family back
together"? It's gold!

28:21.628 --> 28:23.395
Like you didn't do the same thing.

28:23.430 --> 28:25.729
You didn't write a book, John.

28:25.765 --> 28:27.210
You hatched an escape plan.

28:27.246 --> 28:30.367
<i>Do you think I wanted to be on tour?</i>

28:30.403 --> 28:32.730
Living out of suitcases?

28:32.766 --> 28:34.939
Eating crap hotel food?

28:34.974 --> 28:37.208
I don't know. It's a good thing
you weren't too lonely doing it.

28:42.014 --> 28:45.648
Oh, honey. Honey, please, please.

28:45.684 --> 28:47.650
Wherever you're going
right now, I'm just...

28:47.686 --> 28:48.952
I am asking you not to.

29:00.698 --> 29:02.298
