29:02.333 --> 29:03.098
 Come on, baby.

29:03.134 --> 29:04.352
Let me... let me get your number.

29:04.387 --> 29:05.959
Are you deaf and dumb?

29:05.994 --> 29:08.025
- I told you I'm with someone.
- Yeah?

29:08.060 --> 29:09.771
Who?

29:09.807 --> 29:11.240
Him.

29:12.509 --> 29:15.176
You haven't even talked to that guy.

29:15.212 --> 29:16.878
Come on, man.

29:24.027 --> 29:25.786
We don't do a lot of talking.

29:27.290 --> 29:28.146
Shut up.

29:28.181 --> 29:30.225
Man: Mm, mm, mm.

29:30.260 --> 29:31.826
Desperate times. Sorry.

29:31.861 --> 29:34.022
Uh, no. I am happy to help.

29:34.057 --> 29:35.329
Oh, my god.

29:35.364 --> 29:37.331
Danny, you don't recognize me?

29:37.366 --> 29:39.399
Should I?

29:39.434 --> 29:40.868
Bridey Cruz. High school.

29:42.338 --> 29:45.339
Wow.

29:45.374 --> 29:47.674
Yeah, uh, of course.

29:47.709 --> 29:49.041
I'm sorry.

29:49.077 --> 29:50.343
Hey, I watch the news.

29:50.378 --> 29:52.178
You got a lot on your plate right now.

29:54.548 --> 29:57.383
So how is he... your brother?

29:57.418 --> 29:59.352
Uh, he's good. He's good, you know.

29:59.387 --> 30:00.586
I mean, he's got scars,

30:00.621 --> 30:02.621
and it's gonna take a while, but...

30:06.026 --> 30:08.659
Me and my sister were
supposed to be watching him.

30:08.695 --> 30:11.562
I remember.

30:12.632 --> 30:14.766
I was there.

30:17.237 --> 30:19.104
Yeah.

30:21.835 --> 30:23.901
So I guess we all got 'em.

30:24.410 --> 30:26.043
Hmm?

30:28.414 --> 30:30.072
Scars.

