31:55.714 --> 31:56.512
<i>Oka... </i>

31:58.783 --> 32:01.417
Forgive me, father, for I have sinned.

32:12.963 --> 32:14.229
Police!

32:14.264 --> 32:17.032
On your knees, on your knees!

32:18.468 --> 32:21.203
Thought you said it was legal now!

32:21.238 --> 32:23.037
What the... ?

32:26.575 --> 32:30.044
It has been six days
since my last confession.

32:32.081 --> 32:33.280
