<i>I want a big piece!</i>

32:56.937 --> 32:58.237
<i>I want the frosting!</i>

32:58.272 --> 33:00.773
I want a big piece.

33:00.808 --> 33:03.108
I want the frosting.

33:03.144 --> 33:04.810
<i>All right.</i>

33:07.143 --> 33:08.609
I didn't take that little boy's ship.

33:08.645 --> 33:10.592
I don't even know how it got there.

33:11.646 --> 33:12.545
Here's what I think, Hank.

33:12.580 --> 33:14.938
Just 'cause someone does something bad,

33:15.066 --> 33:16.565
it doesn't make them a bad person.

33:16.601 --> 33:19.690
But, see, if this thing goes to trial,

33:19.715 --> 33:21.536
the jury's not gonna see it like me.

33:21.571 --> 33:22.748
Because first, they're gonna hear

33:22.773 --> 33:23.793
about what you did in that park.

33:23.853 --> 33:24.985
That was years ago.

33:25.020 --> 33:27.020
I took my lump for that. I paid a fine.

33:27.056 --> 33:27.821
I registered.

33:27.857 --> 33:29.756
And then they're gonna see this.

33:33.349 --> 33:34.484
What's that?

33:34.509 --> 33:35.762
Your computer.

33:37.477 --> 33:38.758
Want to watch?

33:46.413 --> 33:47.580
Turn it off.

33:47.767 --> 33:48.945
You're the one that likes it.

33:49.592 --> 33:50.518
I just want to know why.

33:50.598 --> 33:51.690
Please turn it off.

33:51.715 --> 33:53.037
Is it because they're
so little and helpless?

33:53.072 --> 33:54.268
Turn it off!

33:57.588 --> 33:59.916
I look at that stuff.

34:00.058 --> 34:02.082
I don't act on it.

34:03.884 --> 34:06.017
I just look at it.

34:06.051 --> 34:07.817
I believe you.

34:07.853 --> 34:08.818
Do you?

34:08.853 --> 34:10.186
But, see, a jury...

34:10.221 --> 34:12.154
They're not gonna see it like me.

34:12.188 --> 34:14.657
They're just gonna see a
monster that likes little boys.

34:14.692 --> 34:17.103
Little boys like Adam Warren.

34:17.862 --> 34:19.364
You didn't mean to kill him.

34:19.400 --> 34:21.129
- Sometimes, things just get out of hand.
- No.

34:21.165 --> 34:23.498
And that's why you cleaned the
garage... To get rid of his blood.

34:23.534 --> 34:25.266
- But you kept his toy to think about it.
- No.

34:25.302 --> 34:26.569
Remember what you did.

34:26.603 --> 34:27.842
- Dream about it.
- No.

34:27.877 --> 34:29.003
Hank, it's not your fault.

34:29.039 --> 34:30.368
You were born this way.

34:30.402 --> 34:33.574
It's like having straight hair or curly.

34:33.610 --> 34:35.208
Blue eyes or freckles.

34:35.244 --> 34:36.878
You can't help the way you were born.

34:36.913 --> 34:38.812
I don't want to be like this.

34:39.916 --> 34:41.552
I can help you.

34:42.886 --> 34:43.851
I can help.

34:44.920 --> 34:46.840
If you just tell me
what you did to Adam.

34:47.730 --> 34:51.331
I won't let them make you their monster.

34:55.464 --> 34:57.798
They're gonna sentence you to death.

34:57.833 --> 35:00.901
Wipe you away, like a stain.

35:00.936 --> 35:01.968
Oh, god.

35:02.003 --> 35:02.902
No, Hank.

35:02.937 --> 35:04.136
There's no god.

35:04.171 --> 35:06.739
'Cause if there was, why would
he make something like you?

35:06.774 --> 35:09.075
- Please...
- There's only me.

35:09.110 --> 35:11.143
I'm the only one that can save you now.

35:12.172 --> 35:14.947
So, tell me about Adam.

35:16.017 --> 35:16.916
Hmm?

35:17.907 --> 35:20.551
Tell me what you did to him.

35:41.992 --> 35:43.280
That bad, huh?

35:44.842 --> 35:46.966
What are you doing here?

35:48.823 --> 35:49.947
I want to help.

35:51.684 --> 35:53.757
Go home, John.

35:53.792 --> 35:55.785
To your son and your wife.

35:55.820 --> 35:57.392
Do you think I have them back now?

35:57.889 --> 35:58.683
John...

35:58.719 --> 36:00.322
I don't have my son back.

36:00.358 --> 36:01.633
Not the sweet little boy

36:01.668 --> 36:05.386
I took my eye off for one damn second.

36:06.031 --> 36:06.896
And my wife?

36:06.931 --> 36:08.667
I'm married to a machine, not a wife.

36:08.774 --> 36:10.372
<i>So the only thing I can do now...</i>

36:10.408 --> 36:12.775
'Cause I sure as hell
can't sleep anymore...

36:12.811 --> 36:15.210
is help you find the
monster who did this to us.

36:15.246 --> 36:16.828
You want to know who
wrecked your family?

36:16.853 --> 36:17.814
So just tell me right now...

36:17.849 --> 36:19.649
- You want to know who the monster is?
- ... how I can help.

36:19.684 --> 36:22.251
<i>I'm the monster.</i>

36:22.286 --> 36:25.254
I'm the one who had it
all figured out at 25

36:25.289 --> 36:27.155
and looked you in the eye

36:27.190 --> 36:28.723
and told you that your son was dead.

36:28.759 --> 36:31.924
Every scar on that kid's
body... It wasn't the bogeyman.

36:31.949 --> 36:33.227
It was me.

36:33.971 --> 36:37.432
I'm the one who stopped
looking and got promoted for it.

36:37.907 --> 36:40.068
So blame me.

36:42.002 --> 36:42.904
Hate me.

36:42.940 --> 36:45.835
Because I'm the one who
didn't save your son.

36:49.979 --> 36:53.647
No. You didn't.

36:57.954 --> 36:59.874
<i>But you saved me.</i>

37:36.303 --> 37:37.603
Where's Dad?

37:37.638 --> 37:41.507
Oh, um, honey, he'll be back soon.

37:41.543 --> 37:43.443
Um, come here.

37:43.478 --> 37:44.511
Let me.

37:44.546 --> 37:46.012
Okay?

37:46.047 --> 37:47.669
Let's see.

37:47.694 --> 37:49.767
Under like this first.

37:50.740 --> 37:52.060
Pull it through.

37:54.814 --> 37:57.207
Better not tell Dad we're doing this.

37:57.374 --> 37:59.742
He's gonna want to teach you himself.

37:59.777 --> 38:01.577
Okay. Okay.

38:01.612 --> 38:03.913
Great.

38:03.948 --> 38:06.520
Put your collar down.

38:14.196 --> 38:15.495
See?

38:16.664 --> 38:18.093
That's a Windsor knot.

38:18.902 --> 38:20.228
 Good morning.

38:20.263 --> 38:21.530
I'll keep this brief.

38:22.034 --> 38:25.566
Let me first begin by thanking
the people of Red Pines

38:25.602 --> 38:27.667
for their overwhelming support.

38:27.703 --> 38:30.570
The medical staff at City Memorial,

38:30.606 --> 38:34.108
everyone at the mayor's
office, and the media,

38:34.143 --> 38:37.111
for allowing us a moment to breathe

38:37.146 --> 38:39.742
and begin the healing process.

38:39.777 --> 38:40.469
Uh...

38:40.494 --> 38:43.359
Family has always been
paramount to who I am

38:43.395 --> 38:45.517
and what I stand for.

38:45.553 --> 38:47.722
And mine got a happy ending.

38:48.222 --> 38:52.689
But we are the exception and
not the rule in this country.

38:54.095 --> 38:55.657
Now more than ever,

38:56.097 --> 38:59.417
I want to strengthen our
child-protection laws,

38:59.611 --> 39:02.196
increase sex-offender monitoring,

39:03.237 --> 39:08.567
fund more programs like AMBER
Alert to protect our children.

39:11.078 --> 39:12.077
To stop the nightmare

39:12.112 --> 39:14.874
that we've been living
for the past 10 years...

39:15.960 --> 39:17.382
From happening...

39:18.587 --> 39:23.949
To other good American families.

39:28.535 --> 39:32.498
So, that is why today, with
the support of my family,

39:32.534 --> 39:36.568
I am announcing my candidacy

39:36.604 --> 39:40.439
for governor of our
great state of Maine.

39:41.775 --> 39:46.378
Not for me, but for my Adam

39:46.413 --> 39:51.415
and for all the other Adams
who are still out there!

40:10.235 --> 40:13.136
We're getting smoked by
every other paper in the country,

40:13.171 --> 40:15.538
like it's their story to tell.

40:15.574 --> 40:17.974
Don't believe everything you read.

40:18.009 --> 40:20.109
What the hell is that supposed to mean?

40:20.145 --> 40:21.611
The doctor at City Memorial

40:21.647 --> 40:23.580
who verified Adam Warren's DNA test.

40:23.615 --> 40:24.446
Mm-hmm?

40:24.482 --> 40:27.783
I called him this morning for comment.

40:27.818 --> 40:29.217
And?

40:29.253 --> 40:31.320
He doesn't exist.

40:34.825 --> 40:36.954
This is our story.

40:37.709 --> 40:39.928
And there's a hell of a lot more to it.

40:50.153 --> 40:51.385
Meyer?

40:51.421 --> 40:53.212
You okay?

40:53.247 --> 40:54.860
Kid's little ship.

40:54.896 --> 40:57.765
Forensics pulled the pedo's
prints off it 10 years ago.

40:57.801 --> 40:58.602
So?

40:58.627 --> 41:00.642
Nina: So that's all they got.

41:00.677 --> 41:02.901
The kid's prints were never on it.

41:02.937 --> 41:04.459
Seems odd, right?

41:04.494 --> 41:06.619
Since he was seen carrying
it around that night.

41:07.895 --> 41:08.960
Unless...

41:08.996 --> 41:14.666
Someone put it in there and
cleaned it for me to find.

41:18.037 --> 41:20.905
<i> They say
every cop has two...</i>

41:20.940 --> 41:23.106
<i>The case that breaks you... </i>

41:24.710 --> 41:26.710
<i>... and the one that makes you.</i>

41:30.282 --> 41:31.081
Oh, gosh.

41:31.116 --> 41:32.749
I've been praying for that family.

41:32.784 --> 41:33.842
They have a long road ahead.

41:33.877 --> 41:35.274
They sure do, ma'am.

41:35.310 --> 41:37.086
They sure do.

